data.description: Welcome to this stunning and meticulously maintained four bedroom, two bathroom home that was built just one year ago in December 2022. Nestled in a lovely neighborhood in Spring Hill, Florida, this home offers convenience, elegance, and modern features that are sure to impress.As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a beautiful KITCHEN boasting GRANITE COUNTERTOPS, sleek gray cabinets, and STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES that perfectly complement the overall aesthetic. The spacious LIVING ROOM offers a side entrance to the LANAI, inviting you to enjoy the outdoors at your leisure.The bedrooms are thoughtfully designed with comfort in mind. The PRIMARY BEDROOM, located to the left of the house, features a large and luxurious bathroom complete with a DOUBLE SINK VANITY, TILE in the wet areas, and a shower adorned with tile that extends all the way up to the ceiling. Additionally, the primary bedroom boasts a generous WALK-IN CLOSET and CEILING FANS for added comfort.The second bedroom is centrally located, providing easy access to all areas of the home, while the two additional bedrooms are situated to the right of the house, ensuring privacy and tranquility. All bedrooms are flooded with natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.Throughout the home, you'll notice the meticulous attention to detail and the tasteful use of neutral colors, with shades of gray and white that create a modern and cohesive aesthetic. The CARPET in the bedrooms adds an extra layer of comfort, while the TILE in the wet areas adds durability and convenience.This home also offers a spacious TWO-CAR GARAGE, perfect for storage or keeping your vehicles protected from the elements. The exterior landscaping has been impeccably maintained, further enhancing the overall appeal of the property.What sets this home apart is the absence of HOMEOWNERS ASSOCIATION (HOA) or COMMUNITY DEVELOPMENT DISTRICT (CDD) restrictions. You have the freedom to personalize and modify your property as you see fit, without the limitations or additional fees often associated with such restrictions. Enjoy the freedom to truly make this house your own, both inside and out.Located in a desirable neighborhood, this home is conveniently situated near all the amenities you could desire. From shopping centers to restaurants, schools, and parks, everything you need is just a short distance away.Don't miss this incredible opportunity to make this beautiful home yours. Call now to schedule a viewing and experience the perfect blend of modern living, comfort, and convenience in this stunning Spring Hill
